{"tid":2272803,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"JYP旗下藝人公開向粉絲索取 「遊戲序號」 ，透露快破產！粉絲不滿：「太超過了吧」","createTime":"2020-11-05T09:43:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-05T13:33:56.000Z","uid":74065,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"90f449d9a9632b9cc9ccf9b0302ed3d443596bb4","tid":2272803,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T09:43:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn1.wishnote.tw/550/2020/11/04/550_1551097_1604479434.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn1.wishnote.tw%2F550%2F2020%2F11%2F04%2F550_1551097_1604479434.webp&h=92c8b5c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n本月3日， JYP 旗下南韓男子組合 DAY6 Jae 在官方認證的個人推特帳號上寫道：「有人能發送 twitch 的代碼嗎？ 我的 twitch 沒有被訂閱或贊助, 這個遊戲有點讓我破產了。」<br />\n<br />\n看見該推文的部分網友們紛紛驚訝道：「是惡作劇嗎？」、「太不像話了吧」、「玩笑開過頭了」、「是被駭了嗎」 等感到震驚的反應。<br />\n<br />\n過去，某位藝人曾公開向粉絲們要求限量版禮物，遭到網友圍攻。 這次 Jae 的發言也讓網友們異口同聲地表示：「想起了過去的事件。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn1.wishnote.tw/550/2020/11/04/550_1551102_1604479456.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn1.wishnote.tw%2F550%2F2020%2F11%2F04%2F550_1551102_1604479456.webp&h=37aad330&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nJae在今年 6 月才在推特表露了對經紀公司不公平待遇的不滿，引起了粉絲們的擔憂。<br />\n<br />\n當時，Jae 提及了自己的 Youtube 頻道時寫道：「 是一邊挨罵，一邊看眼色，一邊請求才勉強得到允許，一個人做了全部的事情，最終因'公司的人不看好我&rsquo;的理由而停掉我的頻道」<br />\n<br />\nJae 還指出:「 爲什麼其他成員都可以在經紀人制作日程表、公司提供費用、公司員工的幫助下進行個人活動呢？」<br />\n<br />\n但是之後 Jae 則改口向大眾解釋：「剛才和公司再次對話後發現有很多誤會，我想表達的部分是公司和我的個人問題，和成員們完全沒有關係。」 另外，先前 DAY6 因部分成員心理狀態不佳而中斷活動。"},{"pid":"eb4c978c13a3de74cf4736322ac13baf51902347","tid":2272803,"uid":259400,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T09:43:51.000Z","msg":"破產師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c536d94542ecc807fa03490dcd3ec390b97fe2c0","tid":2272803,"uid":294121,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T09:46:19.000Z","msg":"韓仔黎講都算柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03544fb86da5b7d80af573a07311ca6176008980","tid":2272803,"uid":15371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T09:57:39.000Z","msg":"入咗JYP係咪人生最大既不幸"},{"pid":"1a3a6d3e02bc3ae3ac78b6f4a485ec4f4fb72ce4","tid":2272803,"uid":212249,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T10:26:46.000Z","msg":"呢隊嘢原來仲未散<br />\n記得有個前成員因為食fans被逼退團<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d74b567a1166ae9b355acabb4af90cef76730d9a","tid":2272803,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1a3a6d3e02bc3ae3ac78b6f4a485ec4f4fb72ce4","tid":2272803,"uid":212249,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T10:26:46.000Z","msg":"呢隊嘢原來仲未散<br />\n記得有個前成員因為食fans被逼退團<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T10:28:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />MORE"},{"pid":"eee59f85dd526e43b03b91ac3f3da67409a81d0c","tid":2272803,"uid":15371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T10:34:11.000Z","msg":"JYP Daddy唔俾遊戲序號佢？"},{"pid":"870ac9a096abe488214a8f5cb148a0fa1954ea35","tid":2272803,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d74b567a1166ae9b355acabb4af90cef76730d9a","tid":2272803,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1a3a6d3e02bc3ae3ac78b6f4a485ec4f4fb72ce4","tid":2272803,"uid":212249,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T10:26:46.000Z","msg":"呢隊嘢原來仲未散<br />\n記得有個前成員因為食fans被逼退團<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T10:28:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png